Test Case 6 — Attendee with no suggestions (Liam Byrne, ID 102)

 * 102 is connected only to 110 (Cian Roche), who has no onward connections
 * Input: Attendee ID 102, degree 2
 * Expected: No networking suggestions found within 2 degrees.

Step 3 — Verify in Neo4j Browser

MATCH path = (a:Attendee {AttendeeID: 101})-[:CONNECTED_TO*2..4]-(s:Attendee)
WHERE NOT (a)-[:CONNECTED_TO]-(s) AND s.AttendeeID <> 101
RETURN s.AttendeeID AS suggested, MIN(length(path)) AS degrees
ORDER BY degrees

Confirm returned IDs match: 115, 103, 120, 106, 104, 114.

